parameters: One time... In a land far, far away, called Inamorta, there
was once a great king of the land.
But one day, the monsters attacked.
An epic battle ensued. But all was lost.
The mighty king was killed, and his civilians taken
... However, the monsters made a huge mistake. They left
the magic crystals behind. These crystals, when all
combined, have the power to annihilate anything in it's way.
They also have the power to heal, but getting them isnt easy
They are hidden in secret locations, scattered around the
city, protected by traps and guards. You must successfully
defeat the traps and all the guards to obtain these. It
But fortunately, two civilians managed to escape capture,
and are willing to sell you some items to help along your
journey. You can collect gold by finding crystals and
Once you have obtained all five crystals, return them to
the king's grave, and he will come back to life.
